            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1446,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01FCbpPZGk8gDrV1ZTMCMZzg\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Hey! No worries—let me catch you up. We're in a brainstorming session to flesh out your business idea so we can build a killer landing page for it. Right now, I'm asking about your core business idea: What does your business do, and what makes it different from competitors?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"A meal prep service that delivers customized, macro-balanced meals for fitness enthusiasts—unlike competitors, we use only local, organic ingredients and adjust macros weekly based on your progress.\\\",\\n    \\\"A B2B software platform that automates invoice processing for accounting firms—we're 10x faster than competitors because we use AI trained specifically on accounting documents.\\\",\\n    \\\"A luxury pet grooming service that comes to your home—we save busy professionals 3+ hours per appointment and use only hypoallergenic, organic products.\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"So, what's your business idea? What problem does it solve, and what's your unique angle?\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2535,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":240,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
