          "headersSize": 573,
          "httpVersion": "HTTP/1.1",
          "method": "POST",
          "postData": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "params": [],
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"output\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"topic\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"summary\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},\"required\":[\"topic\",\"summary\"],\"additionalProperties\":false}}},\"required\":[\"output\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"\\n    <background>\\n      The user and agent have been brainstorming about their business idea.\\n    </background>\\n\\n    <available_topics>\\n      \\\"idea: The core business idea. What does the business do? What makes them different?\\\", \\\"audience: The target audience. What are their pain points? What are their goals?\\\", \\\"solution: How does the user's business solve the audience's pain points, or help them reach their goals?\\\", \\\"socialProof: Social proof or testimonials to include on the landing page. Remember, anything can be social proof: the user's background, experience, beliefs, founder story, etc.\\\", \\\"lookAndFeel: The look and feel of the landing page.\\\"\\n    </available_topics>\\n\\n    <task>\\n      Read the recent chat history, and summarize their answers,\\n      preserving as much information as possible. This will be used to generate \\n      persuasive marketing copy, so be sure to capture all the details.\\n\\n      If the user has answered MULTIPLE topics well, return an array of objects with the following shape:\\n      {\\n          topic: string,\\n          summary: string,\\n      }\\n    </task>\\n    \\n    <chat-history>\\n  <message>... 4 more messages...</message>\\n  <message>assistant: \\\"That's awesome! And what about your solution?\\\"</message>\\n  <message>human: \\\"My fitness program is specifically designed\\\"</message>\\n  <message>assistant: \\\"I see you started answering about your solution! Let me help you flesh that out.\\\\n\\\\nTell me more—how does your fitness program specifically address the challenges these men face? What makes it different from generic fitness programs?\\\\n\\\\nFor example, are you:\\\\n- Modifying exercises for their age and fitness level?\\\\n- Building confidence through small wins?\\\\n- Creating a community of peers?\\\\n- Something else entirely?\\\\n\\\\n```json\\\\n{\\\\n  \\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"reply\\\\\\\",\\\\n  \\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"I see you started answering about your solution! Tell me more—how does your fitness program specifically address the challenges these men face? What makes it different from generic fitness programs?\\\\\\\",\\\\n  \\\\\\\"examples\\\\\\\": [\\\\n    \\\\\\\"We start with beginner-friendly exercises and progressively build strength without injury risk\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"We focus on building confidence through small wins and peer support from other men in their 50s\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"We use a psychology-first approach to overcome the 'too old to get fit' mindset before we even start training\\\\\\\"\\\\n  ],\\\\n  \\\\\\\"conclusion\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"What's the core way your program solves their problem?\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n```\\\"</message>\\n  <message>human: \\\"To help men get started lifting, but using bodyweight exercises, and focusing on injury prevention\\\"</message>\\n</chat-history>\\n\\n    <output>\\n      Return an array of objects with the following shape:\\n      {\\n          topic: string,\\n          summary: string,\\n      }\\n    </output>\\n  \"}]}"
          },
          "queryString": [],
          "url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages"
        },
        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1153,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1153,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01A3KNAUPQqFExdLtcZSS3GD\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01CxsoKAYnTizevcQMcgXYQ5\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"output\":[{\"topic\":\"audience\",\"summary\":\"Men in their 50s who want to get fit but face challenges related to age, fitness level, and confidence. They struggle with the belief that they're 'too old to get fit' and need a program designed specifically for their age group and circumstances.\"},{\"topic\":\"solution\",\"summary\":\"A fitness program specifically designed for men to get started with lifting using bodyweight exercises, with a strong focus on injury prevention. The program addresses the unique challenges these men face by being age-appropriate and safe, helping them build strength without injury risk while overcoming mental barriers about their age and fitness capability.\"}]}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1405,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":189,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
          },
