        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1466,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1466,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_014hFNuSHbWnRR5F1dKDBGcF\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Great! I can see you've got some nice branding for **Launch10** with a rocket/launch theme. Before we dive into the landing page design, I need to understand your business idea better.\\n\\nLooking at your mockups, I can see the visual direction, but I need to hear from you directly: **What does Launch10 actually do? What problem does it solve, and what makes it different from other SaaS tools out there?**\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Tell me about your SaaS tool. What does Launch10 do, and what makes it different?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"Launch10 helps e-commerce founders automate their product launches with AI-powered marketing copy and scheduling\\\",\\n    \\\"Launch10 is a project management tool built specifically for remote teams that syncs across all your tools in one dashboard\\\",\\n    \\\"Launch10 helps indie hackers validate business ideas by running micro-surveys and analyzing competitor data in minutes\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Give me 2-3 sentences about what your tool does and what sets it apart.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":4424,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":255,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
