            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1556,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01VCNryJpxBFf7ppfmPPH6G3\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Great! I can see you've got a solid visual identity with that Launch10 branding. That's helpful context for the look and feel later.\\n\\nBut I still need to understand your **target audience** better so we can write copy that speaks directly to them. \\n\\nAre you primarily targeting:\\n- **Podcast hosts** (who need guests)?\\n- **Podcast guests** (who want exposure)?\\n- **Both equally**?\\n\\nAnd what's their biggest frustration? For example:\\n- Hosts spending hours manually searching for guests?\\n- Guests struggling to get on shows?\\n- Something else?\\n\\nOnce I understand who we're talking to and what problem keeps them up at night, I can help you craft messaging that really resonates.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Let me clarify your primary audience so we nail the messaging. Who are you selling to first, and what's their main pain point?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"Podcast hosts who waste 5+ hours weekly finding guests and want a faster solution\\\",\\n    \\\"Growing podcasters who lack a network and need credible guests to book\\\",\\n    \\\"Both—but we lead with hosts because they're the ones paying\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3393,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":280,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
