            "size": 1343,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_018mUBVfhb8EfB2wcAjgEad4\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I don't see any product photos in your uploads yet. No worries though! You have a couple of options:\\n\\n1. **Upload images now** - Use the Brand Personalization panel on the left to upload your product photos. Once you do, I can use them for the hero section when we build.\\n\\n2. **Build now with smart defaults** - Click \\\"Build My Site\\\" and we'll create your landing page with a professional hero section. You can always swap in your product photos later.\\n\\nWhich would you prefer?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"I don't see any product photos in your uploads yet. No worries though! You have a couple of options:\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"Upload images now using the Brand Personalization panel on the left, then we'll use them for the hero section\\\",\\n    \\\"Build your site now with smart defaults, and you can add your product photos later\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"What works best for you?\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":4233,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":229,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
